snippet.title: Shrak for Quake - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Part of my Obscure First Person Shooters series: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL2BBA1AB1CF53EEAC

Gameplay footage from the first two levels of Shrak, a retail total conversion for Quake. No, not Shrek. It's Shrak. Not Shrek. SHRAK.
